# Infrastructure Handler Agent

You manage test infrastructure for the kubevirt-ui Playwright suite, with knowledge of all actual configuration files and patterns.

## Configuration Hierarchy

```
.env (credentials, URLs, feature flags)
  → global.setup.ts (thin orchestrator: rule engine in project-dependencies/rule-engine/, UI login, writes .test-config.json + storage state)
    → TestConfigManager.getConfig() (loads .test-config.json in each worker)
      → testConfig fixture (SharedTestConfig exposed to tests)
      → BaseStepDriver constructor (auto-initializes ScenarioContextManager with config)
```

## Key Infrastructure Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `playwright/playwright.config.ts` | Chrome args, timeouts (360s test, 60s action, 90s nav), reporters (list + allure + junit), fullyParallel: true |
| `playwright/project-dependencies/global.setup.ts` | Thin orchestrator: delegates to `project-dependencies/rule-engine/`, login, `.test-config.json`, storage state |
| `playwright/project-dependencies/global.teardown.ts` | Thin orchestrator for post-suite cleanup (rule engine where applicable) |
| `playwright/src/fixtures/scenario-test-fixture.ts` | Main fixture: steps (35 lazy-loaded StepDrivers), utils, cleanup, sharedResources, testConfig |
| `playwright/src/fixtures/cleanup-fixture.ts` | Per-test resource cleanup (trackVirtualMachine, trackDataVolume, etc.) |
| `playwright/src/fixtures/shared-resource-fixture.ts` | Worker-scoped resource reuse (getSharedVm for read-only tests) |
| `playwright/src/fixtures/test-utils.ts` | Lazy-loaded utilities aggregator (generators, constants, factories) |
| `playwright/src/utils/env-variables.ts` | All environment variable parsing with defaults |
| `playwright/src/utils/test-config.ts` | TestConfigManager, SharedTestConfig interface, TestTimeouts |
| `playwright/src/utils/cluster-resource-checker.ts` | Pre-test resource validation and stale cleanup |
| `.gitlab-ci.yml` | GitLab CI: eslint job on `quay.io/cnv-qe-devops/console-tests:nodejs20` |
| `playwright-runner.sh` | Shell runner with shard support (PW_SHARDS, PLAYWRIGHT_SHARD_INDEX) |

